    "102933619": {
      "title": "Diffusion of calcium ion liquid slag",
      "abstract": "A simple radioactive tracer technique is used to measure the diffusion coefficient of calcium ion in molten slags. In a slag of 40 pet CaO-40 pet SiO2-20 pet AL2O3, DCa++ at 1450°C is 1.3×10−6 cm2 sec−1."
